articles.author: Lim Hui Jie
articles.title: Asia markets mixed as Japan spending data misses estimates, China's May exports top expectations - CNBC
articles.description: China's May exports beat expectations, climbing 7.6% against the 6% expected by a Reuters poll of economists and vastly higher than the 1.5% rise seen in April.
